{"tid":1851962,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"再發揮香港人力量，social media 洗版！！！","createTime":"2020-01-30T08:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T08:41:31.000Z","uid":269706,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b823c46d31a0395501681eb88419e98bb8fcc042","tid":1851962,"uid":269706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:40:32.000Z","msg":"又係時候重組攻勢！<br />\n<br />\n請向各知名人仕social media 如 IG FB 留言：<br />\n1，五 + 二訴求<br />\n2，只准香港身份證通過所有陸路邊境<br />\n<br />\noption，邊境區域設隔離區，俾有懷疑人仕休息<br />\n<br />\n另一方案，關閉所有陸路口岸，開放新蓮塘口岸，並設隔離區，只准香港身份證通過。<br />\n（你上google map睇下就知蓮塘口岸幾大，而且相傳被捕手足係扣留於該未被使用口岸等送中）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">目標係喚起所有知名人仕既良心，自己香港自己救！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"be847c05556cb7c4fa6a21babd70a695b40756b8","tid":1851962,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:41:31.000Z","msg":"好多tweets需要人<br />\nhome office 排隊 停課留家 之類<br />\n都拎手機禁<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task1 + task2</span></span><br />\n尤其<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task2</span></span><br />\n全部英美議員講野唔過千<br />\n<br />\n已經連續三日都係咁<br />\n跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rLe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=12734daf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task</span></strong></span> 攞任務"}]}